#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
arch-update-popup: System tray updater for Arch Linux.

Runs persistently in the system tray. Checks for updates every 30 minutes
(official repos via checkupdates, AUR via paru/yay) and pre-fetches release
notes in the background before the update window is opened.

Changelog sources tried in order per package:
  1. GitHub Releases API (date + notes)
  2. CHANGELOG.md / NEWS.md from GitHub default branch
  3. GitLab Releases API (gnome/kde/freedesktop/gitlab.com)
  4. Arch packaging GitLab commit message (official repos only)
  5. Version-bump string (final fallback)
"""

